original_title: Country Music Classics: Marty Robbins and Ernest Tubb
overview: Live in 1954 and 1956, Robbins plays 12 songs including "Time Goes By," "I Can't Quit" and more. Tubb plays 14 songs including "So Many Times," "Try Me Once More" and others.
title: Country Music Classics: Marty Robbins and Ernest Tubb
